What Is Rosenpass?
text:
There was a story recently about Rosenpass: https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=34969760

It seems to make VPNs using Wireguard, but I thought Wireguard was already made for VPNs? Clearly I am missing something. But I am about to setup a VPN, so I was hoping someone could shed some light on whether I should consider using Rosenpass instead of straight Wireguard. Any insight appreciated.

text:
